+{"id":"frankenpandas-f3nrr","title":"fd90.267: Expose AggFunc + GroupByOptions + GroupByExecutionOptions","description":"fd90.267: Expose fp-groupby option types + AggFunc to top-level.

fp-groupby has 25 public items unreachable from frankenpandas. Most are internal helper functions (groupby_sum/mean/etc.) for the standalone aggregator API. The user-facing types are:

- AggFunc (enum) — string-dispatch agg fn enum used by groupby_agg
- GroupByOptions — config struct
- GroupByExecutionOptions — execution-tuning struct

The probabilistic data-structure types (HyperLogLog, CountMinSketch, KllSketch, SketchResult, approx_*) are also exposed but more specialized — file separately if needed.

Scope:
- Add 3 user-facing types to top-level fp_groupby re-export
- Skip prelude (config types, less common than DataFrame.groupby())

